# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>After the Jihad stripped many elite units to fill battle armor companies, the LCAF recognized that conventional infantry remained essential for roles that battle armor could not cost-effectively fill. Mechanized tracked platoons deploy from armored personnel carriers that provide protection during movement and allow the formation to keep pace with heavier combat vehicles in offensive operations. Armed with assault rifles and man-portable anti-aircraft weapons, these platoons provide mobile air defense capability that can accompany mechanized formations on the move.</p>
</overview>

